<node><name>Prepare for Class</name>
<id>3</id>
<lefticon>solo</lefticon>
<righticon>reading</righticon>
<column>OOC</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Read two texts: the ﬁrst on the theory of the texte expressif in their workbook and the second is the example of the texte expressif ”Espion demande, rang´ee six”.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
<linkedwf>undefined</linkedwf>
