<node><name>Write a Letter Based on the Readings</name>
<id>5</id>
<lefticon>group</lefticon>
<righticon>write</righticon>
<column>ICS</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;In groups of 4-5, write a paragraph of the development section of the texte expressif in the form of the letter. This text needs to contain components seen during readings, demonstrating comprehension of concepts such as qualifying adjectives and they way they are used in a text.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
