<id>7</id>
<lefticon>group</lefticon>
<righticon>peerreview</righticon>
<column>ICS</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Each member of the group edits each other's language and grammar while working. This is a retroactive self-corrective process that the students do while they write.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
